title: Miele Cooktops: PowerFlex
description:
Miele Cooktops: PowerFlex

Whether cooking with one pot, two pots or a casserole dish, the
flexibility of this unique feature allows for even, powerful heat
throughout the cooking process. Allowing you to combine two
cooking zones into one, Miele's PowerFlex zone is perfect for
large items and helpful when extra power is required.

Abt is a proud authorized retailer of Miele Appliances. Shop for Miele Cooktops as well as the full line of Miele Appliances at Abt today!
